'''前脈絡叢動脈'''（{{lang|en|Anterior choroidal artery}}）一般源自於[[內頸動脈|內頸動脈]]，但某些罕見個案會源自於{{tsl|en|middle cerebral artery|中大腦動脈}}<ref>{{cite book|last=Werner]|first=[senior managing editor Maureen Barlow Pugh ; managing editor Barbara|title=Stedman's medical dictionary.|year=2000|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Williams|location=Philadelphia, Pa. [u.a.]|isbn=0-683-40007-X|edition=27.|chapter=Artery, anterior choroidal}}</ref>

==解剖==
前脈絡叢動脈負責供應端腦、間腦及中腦的構造，包含<ref>{{cite book|last=Ropper|first=Maurice Victor, Allan H.|title=Adams and Victor's principles of neurology|year=2001|publisher=Medical Pub. Division, McGraw-Hill|location=New York|isbn=0-07-067497-3|edition=7th}}</ref>：
* [[侧脑室|侧脑室]]及{{tsl|en|third ventricle|第三腦室}}的[[脈絡叢|脈絡叢]]
* [[视交叉|视交叉]]及{{tsl|en|optic tract|視徑}}
* {{tsl|en|internal capsule|內囊}}
* {{tsl|en|lateral geniculate body|外膝狀體}}
* {{tsl|en|globus pallidus|蒼白球}}
* [[尾状核|尾状核]]尾部
* [[海马体|海马体]]
* [[杏仁核|杏仁核]]
* [[黑质|黑质]]
* {{tsl|en|red nucleus|紅核}}
* {{tsl|en|crus cerebri|大腦腳}}

==臨床意義==
有關本動脈受損或阻塞所造成的影響上未完全明朗，有研究顯示可能會造成對側[[輕偏癱|輕偏癱]]、對側{{tsl|en|hypoesthesia|觸覺遲鈍}}，以及, and {{tsl|en|homonymous hemianopsia|同向偏盲}}。這些症狀可能緣自於{{tsl|en|internal capsule|內囊}}後肢、[[丘脑|丘脑]]、[[视交叉|视交叉]]，及{{tsl|en|optic tract|視徑}}[[缺血|缺血]]。但內囊後支還有源自{{tsl|en|middle cerebral artery|中大腦動脈}}的{{le|豆紋動脈|lenticulostriate arteries}}作為備用血流<ref>{{cite journal|last=Helgason|first=C|author2=Caplan, LR|title=Anterior choroidal artery-territory infarction: Report of cases and review|journal=Arch. Neurol.|year=1986|volume=43|pages=681–686|pmid=3729746|doi=10.1001/archneur.1986.00520070039015}}</ref>。

